{"tid":1451699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"811 警察暴動 Police Riot","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:09:24.000Z","uid":9845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f290ebfb7e1ba9f633eab82628d58a04aa1635","tid":1451699,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:13.000Z","msg":"如果以1968年芝加哥警民衝突事件調查報告作標準，今天香港特區警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">刻意攻擊記者，暴打已經被制服的示威者，在民居街頭對少數示威者狂射催淚彈，高空用橡膠子彈狙擊示威者</span></strong>，通通可以歸類為「警察暴動」（Police Riot）。香港及中共縱容包庇警察暴動，是因為要將抗爭者逮捕及判刑，將抗爭世代徹底鏟除淨盡。香港經歷這漫長的夏天後，我們將迎來全新的「暴政」時代，警察可以隨街搜查，用各種理由拘捕，扣留四十八小時，林鄭月娥會用司法程序來滋擾公民，律政司會全力配合，濫捕濫告來製造恐懼。至於由幕後政治勢力動員出來的流氓黑幫，也正式變成親政府民兵組織，摧毀公民社會、壓制反對力量，香港人，心態上相信未準備好這黑暗時代的降臨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20190809/20745460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F20745460&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaP4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=b1294829\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F20745460&h=9639caa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20190809/20745460</a>"},{"pid":"4d4bf2a6bb861b1884699636e6cee14434267846","tid":1451699,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ce5de994618cb560b483b270ad7d0f434f1479e","tid":1451699,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:09:24.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"}]}